Friday, August 14th 2015 in anticipation of the "Straight Outta Compton" film premiere chronicling the story of the superstar hip-hop group N.W.A., 816ENT/RICHBUMENT & SHOWDOWN PRODUCTIONS present the Premiere Party featuring N.W.A. members, live performances NEVER BEFORE SEEN NWA footage, including live streaming of the event all night via TradioV!
